OL,5, A leading cruise ship company is being 
OL,6, accused of planning to fire more than  
OL,7, 900 staff members if they do not accept
OL,8, new terms and conditions.              
OL,10,FCarnival UK, owner of P&O Cruises and  
OL,11,FCunard, notified authorities of the    
OL,12,F"fire-and-rehire" plan one day after   
OL,13,Fbeginning talks with union members.    
OL,15,FThe Nautilus union said it showed the  
OL,16,Fcruise firm had "no real intention to  
OL,17,Fengage" in meaningful negotiations.    
OL,19,FCarnival UK said it was "categorically 
OL,20,Fnot making any redundancies".          
